        <span id="BookReviewTitle" class="BookReviewTitle">The Practical Guide to Enterprise Architecture</span>
        <div class="ItemDetail">By
          <span id="Authors">James McGovern, Scott W. Ambler, Michael E. Stevens, James Linn, Elias K. Jo, Vikas Sharan</span></div>
